Comments
--------
This procedure synchronizes the dbo.ConfigParam table with the settings required by the current version of the application. If
a record is missing it is added. Where the record exists, it is set to current values. ConfigParams no longer used are
deleted from the table. One MERGE statement is used to carryout all operations.

